# Cosmecca Backend

FastAPI boilerplate with:

- FastAPI application factory
- SQLAlchemy 2.0 async engine/session
- Pydantic v2 settings loaded from `.env`
- Versioned API router and health endpoint

## Quick start

```bash
cd backend
python -m venv .venv
source .venv/bin/activate
pip install -e ".[dev]"
cp .env.example .env
uvicorn app.main:app --reload
```

The API health check is available at `GET /api/v1/health`.
